@jvdillon Could you run jenkins? I think my tests should now pass.

On a related note for improvements, you might want to have a distribution argument for the velocities rather than to always use a fixed Gaussian. 
Even, further following some of the new advances, like https://openreview.net/forum?id=B1n8LexRZ, you can add transformations in as well.
